title: Overcooked.2-PLAZA
description:
Overcooked  returns  with a  brand-new helping  of  chaotic  cooking
  action! Journey back to the Onion Kingdom and assemble your  team of
  chefs in classic couch co-op or online play for up to  four players.
  Hold onto your aprons its time to save  the world  (again!)  Out  of
  the frying pan, into the fire Youve saved the world  from  the  Ever
  Peckish. Now a new threat has arisen and its time to get back in the
  kitchen to stave off the hunger of The Unbread!

  For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/728880/
